    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been babied since day one, kept tucked away in a garage, and there isn't a single scratch or mark to be found. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
