    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in absolute showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, all protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and the 'new car' scent is still subtly present. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been garage-kept since day one and serviced exclusively at the dealership with a complete binder of maintenance records included. It comes with two sets of keys, all original manuals, and a clean title. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning enthusiast to own a perfect, investment-grade example of this model.",
      "price": 46500.0,
