    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, featuring an unblemished exterior finish and a pristine interior that retains its original factory character. Meticulously serviced and mechanically flawless, it offers a rare opportunity for the collector or enthusiast seeking a benchmark example of this model. We invite serious inquiries for a private viewing of this distinguished automobile.",
