    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute dream of a car and honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! This beauty has been my absolute baby\u2014it's in flawless condition inside and out. You won't find a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere. It drives like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure. Come take a look, you're going to fall in love!",
