    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 1993 Mazda RX-7 (FD3S) in true mint condition. This example features the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, exhibiting perfect compression across all chambers. The transition between the primary and secondary Hitachi HT12 turbos is linear and crisp, indicating a perfectly sealed vacuum system. The undercarriage is free of oxidation, preserving the integrity of the aluminum double-wishbone suspension and the Power Plant Frame (PPF) which optimizes drivetrain rigidity. Recent preventative maintenance includes a full cooling system overhaul and Viton apex seal verification. This is a non-modified, numbers-matching survivor that delivers a visceral, high-revving analog driving experience. Pristine interior, original BBS wheels, and flawless paint depth.",
